c: 7
v: 137
t: "assuqunxak xixxibisak sugen mara (israa-iil xaylo kinnuk) Shaam deqsitta baaxóy barkat elle oobisnek ayró mawqaay ayró korma ken nagarsisne, Nabiyow ku Rabbik meqe Qangarah xaganay israa-iil xayloh hee duudeh firqawnaa kee kay marih adal yisbireenimih sabbatah baaxol reedá leeh miroctih yan mara ken abne, firqawnaa kee kay mari qarwaay silaacak bicisak suggu iyyeenim kee buqree kee busaatinik xisak sugeenim bayisneh"